		<h2 class="heading to-animate">About Us</h2>
		<p class="to-animate"><span class="firstcharacter">L</span>ong time ago people used to hunt for food and used to cook at the hunting ground itself, time changed hunting reamined the same but cooking was done in the homes in the <b>kitchen</b> later on we were introduced with markets and shops from where we buy raw food and cook it at our homes. later on we became familiar with resturants and takeaway foods in short a place where we can eat food where we dont have to worry about cooking or anything else. But in foodee we try to mix it up a little we are serving food that is for sure but we deliver food we have an on sight kitchen where we cook up some of thr finest and delicious food that one has ever tasted,</p><p>fodeee is an gateway to a whole new level of food odering system in which we try to provide every possible dishes ever tasted by an Indian that too made by the finest chef that this country has to offer</p>
